Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特典影像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤靜為接近雛菊學習劍道之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊藤靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:59.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}本特典影像是把平日裡為「旋風管家」努力的諸位演員\N當成大小姐讓Staff管家來滿足她們的各種願望（※預算內）的企劃!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的特典影像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  看我穿成這個樣子大家就應該明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛菊的劍道很強  那麼我也來練習一下劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在很興奮  這次還請來了老師來教我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片野老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天呢  由於你是第一次學習劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這大約一個半小時的時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你大概能學習到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能盡量學習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後如果能夠和人比賽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（最終目標是比賽!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:39.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其一  竹刀的持法）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣把竹刀放在右手關節的位置  然後這樣握住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是你右手握住的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…這邊是向前的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後左手的小指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾住竹刀的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  勾住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了在刺的時候不向前滑動  這樣握的話就會滑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那握刀的時候就要保持勾住的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是持刀的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手要貼在肚臍的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙臂是彎曲的姿勢  這裡也會保持放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  竹刀的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀尖的高度和喉嚨的高度相比…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉嚨的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微低一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是手的基本姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其二  基本姿勢·步法）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來學習腳的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳呢  就像平時走路時候的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右腳落地  然後左腳就會抬起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是剛剛抬起瞬間的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是持刀的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前腳就這樣向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後左腳腳後跟是抬起的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候  腳後跟是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣斜過去的話身體就是「半身」的姿勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（半身：劍道中與對手連線稍微傾斜的姿勢）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是直的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兩腳的距離有一些寬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離稍微縮一些  這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是距離過近的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的距離就可以了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前腳腳尖到後腳腳跟大概一步半
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間隔大概是地板的一條左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微  稍微向後一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來這樣  在這個姿勢下聽到「前」的時候就向前邁一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁完這一步之後後腳就貼上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  貼上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是貼上來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這樣的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這樣的姿勢跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是同樣的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在向前邁步時候  右腿的膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右腿的膝蓋不要抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要繃緊  要繃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來練習一下前進和後退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  前  前  後  後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後  前  前  前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後  後  前  前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後  後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下  活動活動肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拿著竹刀就已經…相當辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的時候以為就是這麼打一打  沒想到這麼累
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其三  面擊分解動作）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面擊的分解動作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一的時候  保持這樣的姿勢一直向上抬  左手抬到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  左手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手要抬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬不上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往上抬  再往上抬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬不上去～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往上抬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬不上去～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸直  這裡要伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二的時候  二的時候就打到對方的面部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一完了  二的時候要喊「面」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那稍微練習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從基本姿勢開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  面！
