Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三的時候要保持基本姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一
