Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全不知道自己在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯  很不錯  但手臂要能伸直就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:56.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（其四  面擊）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在這裡的話  「一  二  面」的話是打不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真正要打的時候要向前跳出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣大步邁出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後剛才我們看到的防具大概有二十公斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習的時候相當的累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約練習兩個小時  就能出兩公斤左右的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣  只是像現在一樣空揮就能出那麼多的汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你也指導我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有點緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡緊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些緊  這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
